// C27B-021 (2026-04-25): Bitwise / shift smoke.
// All ops 4-backend identical including the Lax-wrapping shifts.
v1 <= BitAnd[5, 3]()
v2 <= BitOr[5, 2]()
v3 <= BitXor[5, 6]()
v4 <= BitNot[0]()
